called Bread and Roses, they
play a lot in the Bay Area.

00:05:57.200 --> 00:05:59.550
So there are days when
we bring in entertainment

00:05:59.550 --> 00:06:02.837
just for the people
that are at our center,

00:06:02.837 --> 00:06:04.720
but also on Friday nights
